This python code lets you build the glc unpacker module consisting of C++ code and a python interface. Run the code for the platform you want to use, and then install the corresponding python and object code:

Mac
===
./build_and_test.py Mac
cp _glc_unpacker.so glc_unpacker.py /somewhere/useful/portable/server


Windows
=======
./build_and_test.py Windows
cp _glc_unpacker.pyd glc_unpacker.py /somewhere/useful/portable/server


Linux
=======
./build_and_test.py Linux
cp _glc_unpacker.so glc_unpacker.py /somewhere/useful/portable/server
